import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ManagerService } from './manager.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-manager', templateUrl: './manager.component.html', styleUrls: ['./manager.component.css'] }) export class ManagerComponent implements OnInit { employees: any[] = []; constructor(private managerService: ManagerService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.managerService.getEmployees() .subscribe( (data) => { this.employees = data; }, (err: any) => { console.error(err); } ); } }
